Package com.company

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationGUI
    Makes the user interface for program and handles different events happening in the program such as clicking on an specific button , exiting operations and so on .
    ApplicationRepository
    Saves a list of all made requests in the program and makes it possible to have access to them .
    BarPanel
    This is a component in GUI interface panel 2 which is repeated many times .
    DeserializeSettings
    Deserializes an object from Settings class and reads it from the file which it has been serialized into it before .
    FileUtils
    This class controls all of the methods that are associated with files .
    GUIRequest
    This class is used for saving a request in GUI interface and serializing it .
    Input
    Controls the input and sends it to RequestHandler class to make a new request .
    MainConsole
    This is a HTTP Client program which is capable of sending requests and getting responses .
    MainGUI
    This is a HTTP Client program which is capable of sending requests and getting responses .
    Request
    This class is for generating an object for request used in serializing and deserializing .
    RequestHandler
    Makes a new request and sends it with the given method , body , and other settings which has been set up by user ; So it handles a request and has control over it .
    RequestRepository
    Controls over different parts of a request and works like a repository which saves different parts of a request in gui interface.
    SendRequest
    Extends swing worker class and Controls sending a request with using RequestHandler to generate and send a specific request with while using GUI interface .
    SerializeSettings
    This class serializes the Settings class and writes it into a file every time the program runs to read it later .
    Settings
    This class is for saving the settings in the program which needs to be serialized an implements the java.io.Serializable interface .
